<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>This article was written for the 2019 Collaboration Contest with my fellow butterfly and friend, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/n-aepic-fael" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4463776); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4463776&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1608430625" alt="N_Aepic_Fael" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4463776)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/n-aepic-fael" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4463776); return false;">N_Aepic_Fael</a></span>. Being my first ever foray into writing prose, I was absolutely terrified to post this, but thanks to my partner and our critters, it's up on the site and doing pretty well.</p>
<p>Fun Fact: I wrote my portion of the tale while working a 16 hour overnight shift at work, in Notepad because I didn't have WiFi on my laptop, the day the posting period ended for the contest. It was critted and posted that same day.</p>
</div>
